{# Description: Full copy/paste Developer Tools template for Step-3 metadata-stack runtime validation (scheduler + metadata policy + stale root-cause + ESP UX gate). #}
{# Version: 2026.04.29.2 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-04-29 #}

{# =========================
  Meta Stack Step-3 Full Validation (Runtime)
  Purpose:
    - One-shot validation packet for Step 3 (parity re-check / test & assess)
    - Combines scheduler readiness, metadata policy/suppression, stale-source triage,
      HA-authoritative media-class contract checks, and ESP auto-only UX gate checks in one render.
  Usage:
    1) Optional refresh actions before rendering:
       - spectra_ls.validate_metadata_policy
         (recommended payload: `trigger_provider_refresh: true`, `force_refresh: true`, `refresh_reason: step3_reboot_validation`)
       - spectra_ls.validate_metadata_prep
       - spectra_ls.validate_contracts
       - script.ma_send_metadata_to_providers (legacy/direct fallback)
    2) Paste into Home Assistant -> Developer Tools -> Template
    3) Capture output for pre / in / post records
  ========================= #}

{% set invalid = ['', 'none', 'unknown', 'unavailable', 'None', none] %}

{% set s_target_primary = 'sensor.shadow_active_target' %}
{% set s_target_fallback = 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target' %}
{% set primary_has_attrs = state_attr(s_target_primary, 'route_trace') is not none or state_attr(s_target_primary, 'captured_at') is not none %}
{% set fallback_has_attrs = state_attr(s_target_fallback, 'route_trace') is not none or state_attr(s_target_fallback, 'captured_at') is not none %}
{% set s_target = s_target_primary if primary_has_attrs else (s_target_fallback if fallback_has_attrs else s_target_primary) %}

{% set route_trace = state_attr(s_target, 'route_trace') or {} %}
{% set contract = state_attr(s_target, 'contract_validation') or {} %}
{% set metadata_prep = state_attr(s_target, 'metadata_prep_validation') or {} %}
{% set scheduler_validation = state_attr(s_target, 'scheduler_validation') or {} %}
{% set write_controls = state_attr(s_target, 'write_controls') or {} %}

{% set authority_mode = write_controls.authority_mode if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.authority_mode is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set route_decision = route_trace.decision if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.decision is defined else '' %}
{% set contract_valid = contract.valid if contract is mapping and contract.valid is defined else false %}
{% set missing_required = contract.missing_required if contract is mapping and contract.missing_required is defined and contract.missing_required is sequence and contract.missing_required is not string else [] %}
{% set unresolved_required = contract.unresolved_required if contract is mapping and contract.unresolved_required is defined and contract.unresolved_required is sequence and contract.unresolved_required is not string else [] %}

{% set scheduler_verdict = scheduler_validation.verdict if scheduler_validation is mapping and scheduler_validation.verdict is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set scheduler_ready = scheduler_validation.ready_for_scheduler_use if scheduler_validation is mapping and scheduler_validation.ready_for_scheduler_use is defined else false %}
{% set scheduler_blocking = scheduler_validation.blocking_reasons if scheduler_validation is mapping and scheduler_validation.blocking_reasons is defined and scheduler_validation.blocking_reasons is sequence and scheduler_validation.blocking_reasons is not string else [] %}

{% set metadata_verdict = metadata_prep.verdict if metadata_prep is mapping and metadata_prep.verdict is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set metadata_ready = metadata_prep.ready_for_metadata_handoff if metadata_prep is mapping and metadata_prep.ready_for_metadata_handoff is defined else false %}
{% set metadata_checks = metadata_prep.checks if metadata_prep is mapping and metadata_prep.checks is defined and metadata_prep.checks is mapping else {} %}
{% set metadata_values = metadata_prep.values if metadata_prep is mapping and metadata_prep.values is defined and metadata_prep.values is mapping else {} %}
{% set suppression_reason = metadata_checks.now_playing_suppression_reason if metadata_checks.now_playing_suppression_reason is defined else 'n/a' %}
{% set np_fresh = metadata_checks.now_playing_fresh_play_signal if metadata_checks.now_playing_fresh_play_signal is defined else false %}
{% set np_play_stale = metadata_checks.now_playing_playing_without_fresh_signal if metadata_checks.now_playing_playing_without_fresh_signal is defined else false %}
{% set np_paused_stale = metadata_checks.now_playing_paused_without_fresh_signal if metadata_checks.now_playing_paused_without_fresh_signal is defined else false %}
{% set np_long_idle_hidden = metadata_checks.now_playing_long_idle_stale_hidden if metadata_checks.now_playing_long_idle_stale_hidden is defined else false %}
{% set np_track_end_stuck = metadata_checks.now_playing_playing_at_track_end_stuck if metadata_checks.now_playing_playing_at_track_end_stuck is defined else false %}
{% set np_recent_play = metadata_checks.now_playing_recent_play_progress if metadata_checks.now_playing_recent_play_progress is defined else 'n/a' %}
{% set np_recent_paused = metadata_checks.now_playing_recent_paused_progress if metadata_checks.now_playing_recent_paused_progress is defined else 'n/a' %}
{% set np_entity = metadata_values.now_playing_entity if metadata_values.now_playing_entity is defined else states('sensor.now_playing_entity') %}
{% set np_state = states('sensor.now_playing_state') | lower %}
{% set np_title = states('sensor.now_playing_title') %}
{% set np_age_s = metadata_values.now_playing_position_age_s if metadata_values.now_playing_position_age_s is defined else 'n/a' %}
{% set meta_stale_s = metadata_values.meta_stale_s if metadata_values.meta_stale_s is defined else states('input_number.ma_meta_stale_s') | float(45) %}
{% set paused_hide_s = metadata_values.paused_hide_s if metadata_values.paused_hide_s is defined else states('input_number.ma_meta_paused_hide_s') | float(600) %}
{% set np_entity_missing = np_entity in invalid %}
{% set np_title_missing = np_title in invalid %}
{% set np_player_fields_raw = state_attr('sensor.now_playing_entity','player_fields_json') | default('', true) %}
{% set np_player_fields =
  np_player_fields_raw if np_player_fields_raw is mapping else
  ((np_player_fields_raw | trim | from_json) if (np_player_fields_raw is string and (np_player_fields_raw | trim).startswith('{') and (np_player_fields_raw | trim | lower) not in ['unknown','unavailable','none','']) else {})
%}
{% set ma_active_player_raw = state_attr('sensor.ma_active_player_id_resolved','player_json') | default('', true) %}
{% set ma_active_player =
  ma_active_player_raw if ma_active_player_raw is mapping else
  ((ma_active_player_raw | trim | from_json) if (ma_active_player_raw is string and (ma_active_player_raw | trim).startswith('{') and (ma_active_player_raw | trim | lower) not in ['unknown','unavailable','none','']) else {})
%}
{% set ma_handoff_uri =
  (np_player_fields.ma_uri if np_player_fields is mapping and np_player_fields.ma_uri is defined else '')
  if (np_player_fields is mapping and np_player_fields.ma_uri is defined and (np_player_fields.ma_uri | string | trim) not in invalid)
  else (
    (
      ma_active_player.current_media.uri if ma_active_player is mapping and ma_active_player.current_media is defined and ma_active_player.current_media is mapping and ma_active_player.current_media.uri is defined and (ma_active_player.current_media.uri | string | trim | lower) not in invalid
      else (
        state_attr(np_entity, 'media_content_id') if np_entity not in invalid and states[np_entity] is not none else ''
      )
    )
  )
%}
{% set ma_handoff_uri_valid = (ma_handoff_uri | string | trim | lower) not in invalid and ':' in (ma_handoff_uri | string) %}
{% set ma_provider_status = states('input_text.ma_metadata_provider_last_status') %}
{% set ma_provider_response = states('input_text.ma_metadata_provider_last_response') %}
{% set ma_provider_providers = states('input_text.ma_metadata_provider_last_providers') %}
{% set ma_provider_item_uri = states('input_text.ma_metadata_provider_last_item_uri') %}
{% set ma_provider_reason = states('input_text.ma_metadata_provider_last_reason') %}
{% set ma_provider_updated = states('input_text.ma_metadata_provider_last_updated_at') %}
{% set ma_provider_updated_ts = as_timestamp(ma_provider_updated) if ma_provider_updated not in invalid else none %}
{% set ma_provider_age_s = (as_timestamp(now()) - ma_provider_updated_ts) if ma_provider_updated_ts is not none else none %}
{% set ma_provider_visible = ma_provider_status not in invalid or ma_provider_response not in invalid or ma_provider_providers not in invalid %}
{% set ma_provider_parse_hint =
  'dispatch_not_attempted_or_uri_unresolved' if not ma_handoff_uri_valid and not ma_provider_visible
  else (
    'provider_rows_missing_in_response_payload' if ma_provider_providers in ['no_provider_rows_in_response']
    else (
      'request_error' if ma_provider_providers is string and ma_provider_providers.startswith('request_error_')
      else 'ok'
    )
  )
%}

{% set source_now = states('sensor.now_playing_source') | lower %}
{% set source_ma = states('sensor.ma_active_source') | lower %}
{% set app_ma = states('sensor.ma_active_app') | lower %}
{% set source_ctx = source_now ~ ' ' ~ source_ma ~ ' ' ~ app_ma %}
{% set video_hint =
  ('plex' in source_ctx) or
  ('apple tv' in source_ctx) or
  ('appletv' in source_ctx) or
  ('hdmi' in source_ctx) or
  ('tv' in source_ctx)
%}

{% set media_class_raw = states('sensor.now_playing_media_class') %}
{% set media_class = media_class_raw | lower %}
{% set media_class_valid = media_class in ['music', 'non_music', 'none'] %}
{% set display_allowed = is_state('binary_sensor.now_playing_display_allowed', 'on') %}
{% set music_guard_active = is_state_attr('binary_sensor.now_playing_display_allowed', 'music_guard_active', true) %}
{% set preview_key = states('sensor.now_playing_preview_key') %}
{% set preview_key_valid = preview_key not in invalid %}
{% set preview_s = state_attr('sensor.now_playing_media_class', 'non_music_preview_s') | int(30) %}
{% set preview_age_s = (as_timestamp(now()) - as_timestamp(states.sensor.now_playing_preview_key.last_changed)) | float(9999) if preview_key_valid else none %}
{% set media_contract_expected_display =
  true if media_class == 'music'
  else (
    false if media_class == 'none'
    else (
      ((preview_age_s is not none and preview_age_s < preview_s) and not music_guard_active) if preview_key_valid else false
    )
  )
%}
{% set no_audio_video_context_expected =
  video_hint and
  np_entity_missing and
  np_title_missing and
  suppression_reason == 'entity_missing' and
  np_state in ['idle', 'unknown', 'unavailable', 'none']
%}
{% set media_contract_timing_ready = media_class != 'non_music' or (not preview_key_valid) or (preview_age_s is not none) %}
{% set media_contract_display_match = display_allowed == media_contract_expected_display if media_class_valid and media_contract_timing_ready else false %}
{% set media_contract_surface_ready = media_class_valid and states('binary_sensor.now_playing_display_allowed') not in invalid %}
{% set media_contract_unknown_expected_ok = no_audio_video_context_expected and media_class in ['unknown', 'unavailable', 'none', ''] and not display_allowed %}
{% set media_contract_gate_ok = (media_contract_surface_ready and media_contract_timing_ready and media_contract_display_match) or media_contract_unknown_expected_ok %}
{% set media_contract_reason =
  'expected_unknown_no_audio_video_context' if media_contract_unknown_expected_ok
  else (
  'invalid_media_class' if not media_class_valid
  else (
    'surface_missing_or_unknown' if not media_contract_surface_ready
    else (
      'preview_timing_unavailable' if not media_contract_timing_ready
      else (
        'display_gate_mismatch' if not media_contract_display_match
        else 'ok'
      )
    )
  )
  )
%}

{% set metadata_fail_is_expected_no_audio = metadata_verdict == 'FAIL' and no_audio_video_context_expected and suppression_reason == 'entity_missing' %}
{% set metadata_effective_fail = metadata_verdict == 'FAIL' and not metadata_fail_is_expected_no_audio %}

{% set esp_blank_expected = media_class == 'non_music' and not display_allowed %}

{% set esp_handoff = states('sensor.spectra_ls_system_esp_control_handoff_status') %}
{% set esp_target = states('sensor.spectra_ls_system_esp_control_target') %}
{% set esp_oled = states('sensor.spectra_ls_system_esp_oled_status') %}
{% set esp_handoff_ok = esp_handoff not in invalid and esp_handoff in ['ready','pending_refresh','no_target','no_host'] %}
{% set esp_auto_only_gate = is_state('input_boolean.ma_meta_override_active','off') and states('input_text.ma_meta_override_entity') in invalid %}

{% set stale_reason = 'no_clear_reason' %}
{% if np_entity in invalid and np_title in invalid %}
  {% set stale_reason = 'no_active_now_playing_entity' %}
{% elif np_track_end_stuck %}
  {% set stale_reason = 'playing_stuck_at_track_end' %}
{% elif np_play_stale %}
  {% set stale_reason = 'playing_signal_without_fresh_progress' %}
{% elif np_paused_stale %}
  {% set stale_reason = 'paused_without_recent_progress' %}
{% elif np_long_idle_hidden and np_title not in invalid %}
  {% set stale_reason = 'long_idle_entity_carrying_title' %}
{% elif np_fresh %}
  {% set stale_reason = 'fresh_signal_ok' %}
{% endif %}

{% set captured_at = state_attr(s_target, 'captured_at') | default('', true) %}
{% set captured_ts = as_timestamp(captured_at) if captured_at not in invalid else none %}
{% set age_s = (as_timestamp(now()) - captured_ts) if captured_ts is not none else none %}
{% set snapshot_fresh = age_s is not none and age_s <= 300 %}

{% set status = 'PASS' %}
{% if (missing_required | length) > 0 or (unresolved_required | length) > 0 or not contract_valid %}
  {% set status = 'FAIL' %}
{% elif scheduler_verdict == 'FAIL' or metadata_effective_fail %}
  {% set status = 'FAIL' %}
{% elif not media_contract_gate_ok and media_contract_reason in ['invalid_media_class', 'display_gate_mismatch'] %}
  {% set status = 'FAIL' %}
{% elif not scheduler_ready or not metadata_ready or not snapshot_fresh or not esp_handoff_ok %}
  {% set status = 'WARN' %}
{% elif not media_contract_gate_ok %}
  {% set status = 'WARN' %}
{% elif np_track_end_stuck or np_play_stale or np_paused_stale %}
  {% set status = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}

{% set readiness = 'READY' if status == 'PASS' else ('BLOCKED' if status == 'FAIL' else 'CAUTION') %}

### Meta Stack Step-3 Full Validation
- Result: **{{ status }}**
- Readiness: **{{ readiness }}**
- Timestamp: **{{ now() }}**
- Shadow source: **{{ s_target }}**

### Core contract + route
- `authority_mode`: **{{ authority_mode }}**
- `route_decision`: **{{ route_decision if route_decision != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- `contract_valid`: **{{ contract_valid }}**
- `missing_required`: **{{ missing_required | length }}**
- `unresolved_required`: **{{ unresolved_required | length }}**

### Scheduler + metadata gates
- `scheduler_verdict / ready`: **{{ scheduler_verdict }} / {{ scheduler_ready }}**
- `metadata_verdict / ready`: **{{ metadata_verdict }} / {{ metadata_ready }}**
- `metadata_effective_fail`: **{{ metadata_effective_fail }}**
- `metadata_fail_expected_no_audio_context`: **{{ metadata_fail_is_expected_no_audio }}**
- `scheduler_blocking`: **{{ scheduler_blocking if scheduler_blocking | length > 0 else [] }}**

### MA provider handoff readiness
- `candidate_item_uri`: **{{ ma_handoff_uri if ma_handoff_uri_valid else 'n/a' }}**
- `candidate_uri_valid`: **{{ ma_handoff_uri_valid }}**
- Recommended refresh call (component path): **spectra_ls.validate_metadata_policy** with `trigger_provider_refresh=true`, `force_refresh=true`, `refresh_reason=step3_reboot_validation`

### MA provider API response (persisted telemetry)
- `last_status`: **{{ ma_provider_status if ma_provider_status not in invalid else 'n/a' }}**
- `last_providers`: **{{ ma_provider_providers if ma_provider_providers not in invalid else 'n/a' }}**
- `last_response`: **{{ ma_provider_response if ma_provider_response not in invalid else 'n/a' }}**
- `last_item_uri`: **{{ ma_provider_item_uri if ma_provider_item_uri not in invalid else 'n/a' }}**
- `last_reason`: **{{ ma_provider_reason if ma_provider_reason not in invalid else 'n/a' }}**
- `last_updated_at`: **{{ ma_provider_updated if ma_provider_updated not in invalid else 'n/a' }}**
- `last_response_age_s`: **{{ ma_provider_age_s | round(1) if ma_provider_age_s is not none else 'n/a' }}**
- `provider_parse_hint`: **{{ ma_provider_parse_hint }}**

### HA media-class contract (authoritative policy)
- `now_playing_media_class`: **{{ media_class if media_class_valid else ('invalid:' ~ media_class_raw) }}**
- `display_allowed`: **{{ display_allowed }}**
- `preview_key`: **{{ preview_key if preview_key_valid else 'n/a' }}**
- `preview_window_s`: **{{ preview_s }}**
- `preview_key_age_s`: **{{ preview_age_s | round(1) if preview_age_s is not none else 'n/a' }}**
- `music_guard_active`: **{{ music_guard_active }}**
- `expected_display_allowed`: **{{ media_contract_expected_display if media_class_valid else 'n/a' }}**
- `contract_surface_ready`: **{{ media_contract_surface_ready }}**
- `contract_timing_ready`: **{{ media_contract_timing_ready }}**
- `unknown_expected_no_audio_video_context`: **{{ media_contract_unknown_expected_ok }}**
- `contract_gate_ok`: **{{ media_contract_gate_ok }}**
- `contract_reason`: **{{ media_contract_reason }}**

### Stale policy + suppression (dual-threshold)
- `suppression_reason`: **{{ suppression_reason }}**
- `fresh_play_signal`: **{{ np_fresh }}**
- `recent_play_progress`: **{{ np_recent_play }}**
- `recent_paused_progress`: **{{ np_recent_paused }}**
- `playing_without_fresh_signal`: **{{ np_play_stale }}**
- `paused_without_fresh_signal`: **{{ np_paused_stale }}**
- `playing_at_track_end_stuck`: **{{ np_track_end_stuck }}**
- `long_idle_stale_hidden`: **{{ np_long_idle_hidden }}**
- `now_playing_entity/state/title`: **{{ np_entity if np_entity not in invalid else 'n/a' }} / {{ np_state }} / {{ np_title if np_title not in invalid else 'n/a' }}**
- `now_playing_position_age_s`: **{{ np_age_s }}**
- Thresholds: **playing<= {{ meta_stale_s }}s, paused<= {{ paused_hide_s }}s**
- Stale root-cause classification: **{{ stale_reason }}**
- Video/no-audio context expected: **{{ no_audio_video_context_expected }}**
- Source context hint: **{{ source_ctx | trim if (source_ctx | trim) != '' else 'n/a' }}**

### ESP + UX gate
- `esp_control_handoff_status`: **{{ esp_handoff if esp_handoff not in invalid else 'n/a' }}**
- `esp_control_target`: **{{ esp_target if esp_target not in invalid else 'n/a' }}**
- `esp_oled_status`: **{{ esp_oled if esp_oled not in invalid else 'n/a' }}**
- ESP telemetry available: **{{ (esp_handoff not in invalid) or (esp_target not in invalid) or (esp_oled not in invalid) }}**
- Non-music blank expected now: **{{ esp_blank_expected }}**
- Auto-only fallback helpers currently clear: **{{ esp_auto_only_gate }}**

### Snapshot freshness
- `captured_at`: **{{ captured_at if captured_at not in invalid else 'n/a' }}**
- Snapshot age (s): **{{ age_s | round(1) if age_s is not none else 'n/a' }}**
- Snapshot fresh (<=300s): **{{ snapshot_fresh }}**

### Step-3 outcome guidance
{% if status == 'PASS' %}
- Step 3 validation packet is healthy. Record this render as runtime evidence and proceed to closeout packet assembly.
{% elif status == 'WARN' %}
- Step 3 is partially healthy. Resolve WARN surfaces (scheduler/metadata/media-contract freshness or ESP gate) and re-render before closeout.
{% else %}
- Step 3 is blocked. Fix contract/gate failures first (including media-class/display-allow mismatches when present), then re-run this template.
{% endif %}
